  * Pedro Peña Pérez
    - Update installers to include new needed libraries
    - Fix problem with translations in tinymce 3.5.11 popups
    - Fix [#2519]: Error on Debian eXe development package (02/06/2015)
    - Fix problem by which user configured locale is overriden by chooseDefaultLocale if not googleApiClientID is configured
    - Fix chooseDefaultLocale: in Debian systems, localeDir (/usr/share/locale) can contain locale directories without exe.mo, so no choose these dirs
    - Guess correct locale based in user environment when no locale is configured in config file
    - Fix [#2546] Link to https makes eXe crash.
    - Fix [#2661]: Problema en el texto del botón de retroalimentación
    - Fix [#2662]: Write texts in dropdown . Form lom and lom es
    - Force selection of value in combo boxes of Properties->Package tab
    - Fix [#2687]: Ocultar los idevices experimentales.
    - Implement Procomún publication
    - Show nested nodes in epub3 navigation.
    - Fixes [#2806]: "No se mantiene sangrado índices exportaciones epub3"
    - Add checkers to detect duplicated idevice ids and wrong idevice next id.
    - Fixes [#2763]: Comportamiento extraño en idevice
    - Allow any iso 8601 date time format for datetime fields in lom/lom.es metadata.
    - Fixes [#2710] Caso extraño en importados de metadatos
    - Set correct language when inserting an empty optional field in lom metadata form.
    - Fixes [#2793] Bug metadatos lom-es
    - Fix wrong file format error opening elp without idevices
    - Allow to set empty value for license: "(void)"
    - Don't show license footer when no license setted (for example with old package versions)
    - Fixes [#2758]: License problem and [#2655]: The package license can't be deleted
    - Fix style creation in some browsers
    - Fix epub3 table of contents nesting
    - Escape xml entities when exporting LOM and LOM-ES metadata (Fixes #22).
    - Preserve first html filename when uniquifying html file names for exports (Fixes #18).
    - Replace some forja.cenatic.es links
    - Replace some 127.0.0.1 references with exeAppUri (Fixes #20)
    - Fallback to english locale if not locale autodetected
    - Configure pybabel to catch more strings to translate (Fixes #26).
    - Calculate exeAppUri after server initialization (found free port) (Fixes #19).
    - Add exe/tools to Mac OS X package (Fixes #25).
    - Don't try to autodetect encoding of config.xml of a style until default decode error (Fixes #27).
    - Move LOM.es classification sources file to github (Fixes #28).
    - Don't close and clear client handle on connection failure (Fixes #23).
    - More reliable styleIdFromName (Fixes #27).
    - Encode file name urls of files added to a style (Fixes #31).

